WEBVTT

1
01:48:39.295 --> 01:48:41.058 
[sobbing]

2
01:48:40.630 --> 01:48:45.177 
啊！关上门！你关门之后，来陪我哭吧
Oh, shut the door,and when thou hast done so,

3
